<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Light mode styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #F0F0D7; 
            color: #4A5A6B; 
        }

        h1, h2, h3, h4 {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #5D8736; 
        }

        p, ul, li {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #4A5A6B; 
        }

        .lead {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #AB886D; 
        }

        .section-title {
            color: #5D8736; 
            font-size: 2.5rem; 
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .section-content {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #A7C89E; 
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

            .section-content:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px); 
                box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); 
                background-color: #8A9C76; 
            }

        .hero-section {
            background-color: #A7C89E; 
            color: #FFFFFF; 
            padding: 80px 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease; 
        }

            .hero-section:hover {
                background-color: #8A9C76; 
            }

            .hero-section h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                font-weight: 700;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .hero-section .lead {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                color: #FFFFFF; 
            }

        .features-list ul {
            list-style-type: disc; 
            padding-left: 20px; 
        }

        .features-list li {
            font-size: 1.1rem; 
            padding: 10px 0; 
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #AB886D; 
            border-color: #AB886D;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

            .btn-primary:hover {
                background-color: #8A6D56; 
                border-color: #8A6D56;
            }

        /* Grid layout for team members */
        .team-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .team-member {
            background-color: #A7C89E;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
            color: #4A5A6B; 
        }

            .team-member:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                background-color: #8A9C76; 
            }

        /* Grid layout for features */
        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .feature-item {
            background-color: #A7C89E; 
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
            color: #4A5A6B; 
        }

            .feature-item:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                background-color: #8A9C76; 
            }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #243642; 
            color: #FFFFFF; 
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        /* Dark mode */
        body[data-theme="dark"] {
            background-color: #243642; 
            color: #FFFFFF; 
        }

            body[data-theme="dark"] .section-content {
                background-color: #387478; 
            }

            body[data-theme="dark"] .hero-section {
                background-color: #387478; 
                transition: background-color 0.3s ease; 
            }

                body[data-theme="dark"] .hero-section:hover {
                    background-color: #2C5C5F; 
                }

            body[data-theme="dark"] .section-title {
                font-size: 3rem; 
                color: #FFFFFF; 
            }

            body[data-theme="dark"] .features-list li {
                color: #FFFFFF; 
            }

            body[data-theme="dark"] .hero-section h1,
            body[data-theme="dark"] .hero-section .lead,
            body[data-theme="dark"] .container p {
                color: #FFFFFF; 
            }

            body[data-theme="dark"] .team-member {
                background-color: #387478; 
                color: #FFFFFF;
            }

                body[data-theme="dark"] .team-member:hover {
                    background-color: #2C5C5F; 
                }

            body[data-theme="dark"] .feature-item {
                background-color: #387478; 
                color: #FFFFFF; 
            }

                body[data-theme="dark"] .feature-item:hover {
                    background-color: #2C5C5F; 
                }
    </style>
</head>
<body data-theme="dark">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="hero-section">
        <h1 class="display-4">Keep track of what you love.</h1>
        <p class="lead">Only with Trackxd.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <p>
            Welcome to <strong>Trackxd</strong>, developed by Group 7, in compliance with the final project requirements for Application Development (COMP 019) in the BSCS 3-2 block:
        </p>
        <div class="team-grid">
            <div class="team-member">Daquioag, Ace</div>
            <div class="team-member">Lopez, Jenna Mae C.</div>
            <div class="team-member">Manapsal, Kevin C.</div>
            <div class="team-member">Siapengco, Yoj M.</div>
            <div class="team-member">Soliven, Prince Bryll</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h3 class="section-title">Features</h3>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4 class="section-title" style="font-size: 1.75rem;">Home Tab:</h4>
                <ul class="features-list">
                    <li>Easily log the media you’ve completed (movies, TV shows, books).</li>
                    <li>Add new entries with a single click.</li>
                    <li>Keep your collection up to date and organized.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4 class="section-title" style="font-size: 1.75rem;">View List Tab:</h4>
                <ul class="features-list">
                    <li>Browse through your media collection.</li>
                    <li>Stay on top of what you’ve watched, read, or plan to revisit.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>